OL,3,CCarmarthenshire Council stops fridge
OL,4,Crecycling amid storage crisis
OL,6,FCarmarthenshire County Council has
OL,7,Ftold residents that fridges, freezers
OL,8,Fand other cooling appliances can no
OL,9,Flonger be accepted at any of the
OL,10,Fcounty's recycling centres until
OL,11,Ffurther notice.
OL,13,FThe council says the temporary
OL,14,Fsuspension comes as recycling centres
OL,15,Facross Carmarthenshire have reached,
OL,16,Fand even exceeded, their safe storage
OL,17,Fcapacity for refrigeration appliances.
OL,19,FIt says "ongoing disruption" at
OL,20,Fexternal treatment facilities is to
OL,21,Fblame.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
