OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784060308
OL,3,CCarmarthenshire Council stops fridge
OL,4,Crecycling amid storage crisis
OL,6,FResidents have been asked not to bring
OL,7,Fthese items to recycling centres, as
OL,8,Fsites will be unable to accept them.
OL,10,FCarmarthenshire County Council's
OL,11,FCabinet Member for Transport, Waste
OL,12,Fand Infrastructure, Cllr Edward Thomas
OL,13,Fsaid:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
