OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784060308
OL,3,CCarmarthenshire Council stops fridge
OL,4,Crecycling amid storage crisis
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, circumstances beyond
OL,7,Four control have resulted in a
OL,8,Ftemporary disruption to the collection
OL,9,Fand processing of refrigeration
OL,10,Fappliances. Our recycling centres have
OL,11,Fnow reached their storage limits for
OL,12,Fthese items, and we have had to
OL,13,Fsuspend acceptance until further
OL,14,Fnotice.
OL,16,F"We understand this will cause
OL,17,Finconvenience for some residents and
OL,18,Fwould like to thank them for their
OL,19,Fpatience and cooperation while we work
OL,20,Fwith our partners to resolve the
OL,21,Fsituation."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/3
